{"tid":2407341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"初步估算赤字達 3000 億元　創歷史新高　陳茂波強調「睇餸食飯」未承諾派錢","createTime":"2021-02-14T03:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T05:06:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8fea468aff48ae97d5a66796664134c1ca0c3b28","tid":2407341,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"下一財政年度的《財政預算案》將於本月 24 日公佈，財政司司長陳茂波今早在電台節目表示，初步估算 20/21 財政年度赤字會達歷史性新高的 3,000 億元，但他估計受惠股市暢旺，印花稅收入增加，收入預算會有少少落差，估計赤字可能會下跌。對於外界期望派糖，陳茂波強調「睇餸食飯，應洗則洗」，又指再次推出現金派發計劃有一定難度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97%E9%81%94-3000-%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF-%E7%9D%87%E9%A4%B8%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF-%E6%9C%AA%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E7%25AE%2597%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%2581%2594-3000-%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%25A4%25B8%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLudagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=57dd1b8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E7%25AE%2597%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E9%2581%2594-3000-%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%25A4%25B8%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%2F&h=b95b